<div id="review_2305201508" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2305201508" />
    <a title="Peter (on semi-hiatus)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/63168028-peter-on-semi-hiatus"><img alt="Peter (on semi-hiatus)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1516912354p2/63168028.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2305201508?book_show_action=true">Feb 22, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Peter (on semi-hiatus)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Peter (on semi-hiatus)" href="/user/show/63168028-peter-on-semi-hiatus">Peter (on semi-hiatus)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/63168028-peter-on-semi-hiatus?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2305201508" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3449867134518345922"><b> Achievement </b><br/>Genghis Khan’s armies know no bounds and they extend their empire in all directions. West to Europe and Russia, South into Persia and India, and holding onto the Chin territories in the East. The Mongolians are a united nation with Genghis’ families ever growing, with his children now generals Don’t they say that 1 in every 200 people alive today are descendant of Genghis Khan.<br/><br/>This is an epic story to rival all others and it is told at a pace that is fast and exhilarating. The battl</span>
  <span id="freeText3449867134518345922" style="display:none"><b> Achievement </b><br />Genghis Khan’s armies know no bounds and they extend their empire in all directions. West to Europe and Russia, South into Persia and India, and holding onto the Chin territories in the East. The Mongolians are a united nation with Genghis’ families ever growing, with his children now generals Don’t they say that 1 in every 200 people alive today are descendant of Genghis Khan.<br /><br />This is an epic story to rival all others and it is told at a pace that is fast and exhilarating. The battles scenes are depicted in great nail-biting detail, and the politics and tensions are superbly explored.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3449867134518345922" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


